metadata.name: Lick Them #1
metadata.description: A mad scientist has created an interesting mutant. This mutant was a strange mouth endowed with special properties. But he noticed something. This creature always ate one thing, so he started experimenting with more and more mutants, maybe he would discover something new in them. Each creature have different characteristics, but the structure that created the creatures exploded at 10,000. Among them was a rare mutant who was nicknamed "numero uno", he eats the rarest object.
